            <thetext>In the demo:Showcase, select Internal window. Click the button to make the First modal dialog appear. Press TAB keys will make the focus remain within First modal dialog.

Then, click the maximize button in the First modal dialog. The dialog will occupy the whole client area of browser. 

Now, press TAB key several times. Then click the restore button to make the First modal dialog back to the original size. 

Press TAB keys again will see the focus on other windows.</thetext>
